code: public Producer createProducer() throws Exception {     ObjectHelper.notNull(configuration, "configuration").     return new GangliaProducer(this, getPublisher()). }
public Consumer createConsumer(Processor processor) throws Exception {     throw new UnsupportedOperationException("Ganglia consumer not supported"). }

public synchronized Publisher getPublisher() {     if (publisher == null) {         GMetric gmetric = configuration.createGMetric().         publisher = new GMetricPublisher(gmetric).     }     return publisher. }
